                    <span>A bit repitious but informative just the same. It has allowed others to gain an insight into the mental condition of the main perpetrators during thier trial and subsequent sentencing. I shows clearly that these terrible people were little more than thugs who used thier new found power to the detrement of millions.</span>
                  
              
